OL,3,CShepherd's fields littered with sheep
OL,4,Cbones after dead animals left to rot
OL,6,FA shepherd from Oxfordshire who left
OL,7,Fdead sheep to rot in his fields has
OL,8,Fbeen sentenced for animal welfare and
OL,9,Ffarming standards offences.
OL,11,FJonathon Hornsby Simpson, 39, who
OL,12,Ftrades as Jon's Shepherding, had
OL,13,Falready been convicted in April 2023
OL,14,Fof 13 animal welfare and farming
OL,15,Fstandards offences.
