OL,3,CShepherd's fields littered with sheep
OL,4,Cbones after dead animals left to rot
OL,6,FPreviously, the court heard Simpson
OL,7,Fhad failed to comply with restrictions
OL,8,Fon animal byproducts by disposing of a
OL,9,Flarge number of dead sheep over many
OL,10,Fyears, burying them in a muck heap to
OL,11,Frot and decay.
OL,13,FSimpson, formerly of Meadow Bank,
OL,14,FFaringdon, also failed to keep
OL,15,Fadequate records such as an up to date
OL,16,Fregister of animals, records of animal
OL,17,Fmovements and a record of veterinary
OL,18,Fmedicines.
