OL,6,FHe was previously sentenced to a 12
OL,7,Fmonth community order, including
OL,8,Fcompletion of a 15 day rehabilitation
OL,9,Frequirement.
OL,11,FHe was also ordered to pay #2,000
OL,12,Ftowards the prosecution's costs as
OL,13,Fwell as thousands of pounds for the
OL,14,Fappropriate removal of the muck heap
OL,15,Fand animal byproducts.
