OL,3,CShepherd's fields littered with sheep
OL,4,Cbones after dead animals left to rot
OL,6,FDuring a further inspection on 9
OL,7,FOctober 2023, trading standards
OL,8,Fofficers found that no improvements
OL,9,Fhad been made and that Simpson had
OL,10,Ffailed to act on any of the court's
OL,11,Ffindings or advice.
OL,13,FDead sheep were still not being
OL,14,Fdisposed of correctly and were being
OL,15,Fleft to rot in his fields which were
OL,16,Flittered with sheep bones.
