OL,6,FHis Honour Judge Pringle KC sentenced
OL,7,FSimpson to a seven month custodial
OL,8,Fsentence suspended for two years,
OL,9,Ffollowing a hearing at Oxford Crown
OL,10,FCourt on Friday 17 January 2025.
OL,12,FJody Kerman, Oxfordshire County
OL,13,FCouncil's Head of Trading Standards,
OL,14,FPrevention and Protection, said: "The
OL,15,Fvast majority of farmers work to the
OL,16,Fhighest standards, we will continue to
OL,17,Fsupport them.
