OL,4,Cbones after dead animals left to rot
OL,6,F"The small minority who seek to bypass
OL,7,Fthe rules not only put the integrity
OL,8,Fof the food chain at risk and increase
OL,9,Fthe risk of disease spread, but also
OL,10,Fgain an unfair advantage over our
OL,11,Fhardworking farmers.
OL,13,F"As one of the most rural counties in
OL,14,Fthe southeast of England, an
OL,15,Funcontrolled animal disease outbreak
OL,16,Fwould have a hugely damaging impact on
OL,17,Fpeople's lives and our local economy.
OL,19,F"Simpson's sheer ignorance and total
OL,20,Fdisregard for the law could have had
OL,21,Fdire consequences.
